meta_description: West Chester 4040M 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
description: West Chester 4040M 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
short_description: This 2 piece splash suit is specifically designed to keep water out. The rainsuit is constructed with .35ml PVC on polyester with hook and loop closures on all openings to provide a watertight seal.  Jacket has an attached hood with hook and loop chin strap. Four-snap front closure with hook and loop storm flap, open wrists with adjustable hook and loop closures with a drawstring at the waist. Overalls have open ankles with adjustable hook and loop closures. Adjustable elastic suspenders with center thumb cam buckles. Side snaps for sizing. Snap-on neck guard for added protection.
summary: Applications: Pressure Washing Environmental cleanup concrete work
